<plot>Steve, the leader of a local gang apprehends a neo-Nazi skinhead because he has attacked two of his black teenage friends in a nearby alley. The police arrive and take statements from Steve and the two teenage boys. Malcolm, the skinhead, lies unconscious. As we are taken backwards through the story we realise that perhaps the boys aren't telling the whole truth and things may not be as 'Black &amp; White' as they appear.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?050398</url></doc>
